The '''Toprawa Relay Station''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]]-run communications center located on the restricted planet of [[Toprawa/Legends|Toprawa]].

It was here that a contingent of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] transmitted the technical plans for the first [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star]] to [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Princess Leia]] aboard the [[CR90 corvette/Legends|Corellian corvette]] [[Tantive IV/Legends|Tantive IV]]. These Rebels, consisting of [[Red Hand Squadron]] under the leadership of [[Bria Tharen]], held out at the station against Imperial counterattacks until finally being overrun; in the process, the relay station was almost completely destroyed. Those who were not killed in the fighting committed suicide so as not to betray their true mission.

